_json.description: Laura Ashley The Tea Room is located in the Drawing Room and Parlour of the main hotel with additional seating outside on the terrace. The beautiful rooms will serve delicious afternoon tea as well as brunch, made using local produce inspired by the seasons with both modern and traditional dishes included. Guests will enjoy delicate finger sandwiches such as smoked salmon & dill and cream cheese & cucumber, alongside light and fluffy scones served with clotted Devonshire cream and berry jam, all
